divs: Sighting Detailswe were in a softball game, about 100 persons, and we saw this huge, thing flying very low, going very fast, we all were shock, it was unbelievable, we began talking trying to give a explanation to what we saw but, to date we all about a 100 people are convince that we saw an ufo. one thin i have to say is that the flying thing didn't make any noise, and also the wind resistance that was making was amazing, the wind hit us very hard, i have to say that i don't believe in this thing, but this was very amazing.
